AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 564* House Bill No. 803
by inserting the following new section immediately preceding the penultimate section and
renumbering the subsequent sections accordingly:
SECTION ___. This act does not apply in counties having a population of not less than
two hundred forty-seven thousand seven hundred (247,700) nor more than two hundred forty-
seven thousand eight hundred (247,800), according to the 2020 federal census or any
subsequent federal census.
